Package org.rplgleparser.api.LFLD

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FLDLoutputFormat
    A marker interface used to generically handle all the FLDL* interfaces
    IFLDL0100
    Public interface of classes that implement the IBM QUSLFLD FLDL0100 interface.
    IFLDL0200
    Public interface of classes that implement the IBM QUSLFLD FLDL0200 interface.
    IFLDL0300
    Public interface of classes that implement the IBM QUSLFLD FLDL0300 interface.
    IHeaderSection
    Public interface of classes that implement the IBM QUSLFLD Header Section interface.
    IInputParameterSection
    Public interface of classes that implement the IBM QUSLFLD Input Parameter Section interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FLDL0100
    A data transfer object with conversion capabilities from AS400 Byte[].
    FLDL0200
    A data transfer object with conversion capabilities from AS400 Byte[].
    FLDL0300
    A data transfer object with conversion capabilities from AS400 Byte[].
    HeaderSection
    Implementation class for the header section of the QUSLFLD api.
    InputParameterSection
    A data transfer object with conversion capabilities from AS400 Byte[].
    ObjectListToArrayList
    An example of how to extend the QUSLFLD class to do some arbitrary thing, in this case writing the basics of a DDS source member from the metadata returned.
    QUSLFLD
    This is the main workhorse class for calling the QUSLFLD API.
